| ðŸ“š Sequence | `list`       | Ordered, changeable, allows duplicates   | `nums = [1, 2, 3]`                     |
|             | `tuple`      | Ordered, **unchangeable**, duplicates OK | `colors = ('red', 'blue')`             |
